\subsection {{asSnakeCaseLower parent.label}}_attr_{{asSnakeCaseLower label}} {{parent.label}}/{{label}} Attribute

**MQTT Topic Pattern:**

```
[PREFIX]/{{asPublicationName parent.label}}/Attributes/{{label}}/Reported
[PREFIX]/{{asPublicationName parent.label}}/Attributes/{{label}}/Desired
```

**MQTT Payload JSON Schema:**

```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "title": "{{asPublicationName parent.label}} Cluster {{label}} Attribute Properties",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "value": {
{{#if (isMonotonousArray label)}}
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "{{asJSONType type label parent.label}}"
      }
{{else}}
      "type": "{{asJSONType type label parent.label}}"
{{/if}}
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "value"
  ]
}
```


**Example Mosquitto CLI Tool Usage**

To see desired/reported value for {{label}} attribute under the by-unid topic space:

```console
mosquitto_sub -t 'ucl/by-unid/+{{#unless (clusterWithoutEndpoints parent.label)}}/+{{/unless}}/{{asPublicationName parent.label}}/Attributes/{{label}}/+'

# Example output
{{#if (isMonotonousArray label)}}

ucl/by-unid/<UNID>{{#unless (clusterWithoutEndpoints parent.label)}}/ep0{{/unless}}/{{asPublicationName parent.label}}/Attributes/{{label}}/Desired { "value": [<DESIRED_{{asSnakeCaseUpper label}}>,<DESIRED_{{asSnakeCaseUpper label}}>]}
ucl/by-unid/<UNID>{{#unless (clusterWithoutEndpoints parent.label)}}/ep0{{/unless}}/{{asPublicationName parent.label}}/Attributes/{{label}}/Reported { "value": [<REPORTED_{{asSnakeCaseUpper label}}>,<REPORTED_{{asSnakeCaseUpper label}}>]}

{{else}}

ucl/by-unid/<UNID>{{#unless (clusterWithoutEndpoints parent.label)}}/ep0{{/unless}}/{{asPublicationName parent.label}}/Attributes/{{label}}/Desired { "value": <DESIRED_{{asSnakeCaseUpper label}}>}
ucl/by-unid/<UNID>{{#unless (clusterWithoutEndpoints parent.label)}}/ep0{{/unless}}/{{asPublicationName parent.label}}/Attributes/{{label}}/Reported { "value": <REPORTED_{{asSnakeCaseUpper label}}>}

{{/if}}
```

